data.description: This is a well maintained home in a lovely, gated, northside community. The owners retreat and 2 other bedrooms are downstairs. Upstairs you will find a large gameroom, a fourth  bedroom and one full bathroom. There are high end features, such as rounded corners, art niches and a fireplace to cozy up to in the winter. Out back there's a nice sized covered patio as well as a large storage shed. The subdivision is gated and features a playground a swimming pool and even a lake. You can fish in the lake according to a neighbor. She said it's full of bass, and I quote... "Big ones!"  Be sure to check out the virtual tour above.
